"{\"uid\": \"newsus.cgtn.com-news-2024-08-07-Olympic-hammer-thrower-Ethan-Katzberg-on-being-called-Thor--1vRjORWFww8-p.html\", \"text\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use. You can change your cookie settings through your browser.  Dan Williams  Copied  Canada\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Ethan Katzberg might not be a household name for many, but he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s celebrating becoming the youngest ever men\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Olympic hammer throw gold medalist. Added to that, the image of him in action has been compared to that of another hammer wielding superstar, the Marvel comic book character Thor. CGTN\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Dan Williams caught up with Katzberg in Paris.  For more, check out our exclusive content onCGTN Nowand subscribe to our weekly newsletter,The China Report.  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\"}"